  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee or oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 2-3 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add the sliced leeks and cook for 5-7 minutes until tender.",
    "Add the chopped cilantro, thyme, salt, and black pepper. Stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the berbere spice blend and paprika. Stir for 30 seconds.",
    "Add the butter or ghee and stir until melted.",
    "Reduce heat to low and create a well in the center of the pan.",
    "Add 2 tablespoons of clarified butter or ghee to the well and stir until molten.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
